---
const { backgroundColor = '', contentColor = 'text-primary-content' } =
  Astro.props;
---

<section
  class:list={[
    'relative py-20 px-4 text-center overflow-hidden',
    backgroundColor || 'bg-primary',
    contentColor,
  ]}
>
  <!-- Decoración de fondo: círculos difuminados -->
  <span
    class="absolute -top-10 -left-10 w-56 h-56 rounded-full bg-white/10 blur-2xl pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <span
    class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-72 h-72 rounded-full bg-secondary/20 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"></span>
  <!-- Patas decorativas -->
  <span
    class="absolute top-6 right-12 text-4xl opacity-20 rotate-12 select-none pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true">🐾</span
  >
  <span
    class="absolute bottom-6 left-10 text-3xl opacity-15 -rotate-6 select-none pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true">🐱</span
  >

  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center gap-7 relative z-10">
    <slot name="text">
      <div>
        <h2
          class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-tight mb-4 leading-tight"
        >
          Cada vida cuenta,<br />¿nos echas una patita?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl font-medium opacity-90">
          Muchos gatos necesitan tu ayuda. Con tu apoyo podemos seguir
          rescatando, cuidando y encontrando hogares para ellos.
        </p>
      </div>
    </slot>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 w-full justify-center">
      <slot name="actions">
        <a
          href="/adopta"
          class="btn btn-secondary btn-lg w-full sm:w-auto rounded-full font-extrabold px-9 shadow-lg"
        >
          Adopta un gato
        </a>
        <a
          href="/colabora"
          class="btn btn-outline btn-lg w-full sm:w-auto rounded-full font-bold px-9 border-white/60 text-white hover:bg-white/20 hover:border-white"
        >
          Haz una donación
        </a>
      </slot>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
